Package com.hhstechgroup.common

This Package is collection of different classes as like BaseActions, DataProviderForProviderInfo, EnrollmentAndCoC, HomePage, InboxIU, Login, Reports etc.,
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseActions
    BaseAction is provided as an intermediate class for shared functionality between action and any stock implementation provided in this package.
    CalendarPopUp
    This class enables interaction with a calendar popup.
    Coc
    This class supports the creation, population and navigation of Provider Change Of Circumstance (CoC) requests.
    Data
    Data class contains all the public static final Strings available to all instances of the class and to other objects using the Data class
    DataFiles
    DataFiles class is used to read data from a file.
    DataProviderForProviderInfo
    This class utilizes DataProviders to pass Provider Info to tests scripts
    DataProviders
    This class utilizes DataProviders and methods to pass Provider Info to tests scripts
    Email
    Email class provides all the functionality of email configuration
    EnrollmentsAndCoc
    EnrollmentsAndCoc class provides functionalities related to enrollments and change of circumstances.
    HomePage
    HomePage class provides all the functionalities in the home page of DYP application
    InboxIU
    InboxIU class provides the functionality of internal user message section
    Locators
    Locators class contains all the locators in DYP application through multiple ways of locating an element such as xpath, cssSelector.
    Login
    Login class is provided as an intermediate class for shared functionality between action and any stock implementation provided in this package.
    Providers
    Providers class contains a number of useful miscellaneous methods to get provider's info which are generally informational and would be used accordingly.
    Reports
    Reports class is used to generate HTML reports.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Permissions
    Permissions class represents a group of constants (unchangeable variables)
    PermissionsSections
    PermissionsSections class represents a group of constants (unchangeable variables)
    Roles
    Roles class represents a group of constants (unchangeable variables)
